Machakos Governor Alfred Mutua Has Today Recorded A Statement With The Police Claiming His Life Is In Danger. Mutua Alleges That The Deputy President William Ruto, The Leader Of Majority In The National Assembly Aden Duale And The Leader Of Majority In The Senate Kipchumba Murkomen Have On Various Occassions Threatned Unspecified Consequences Because Of His Statements On National Issues.